Feature: League Ranking
    
    # The example has three steps
    Scenario: As an athlete in a league, I want to view the historical rankings 
              registered in it to keep me informed about the scores of the competitions
        Given: an athlete, who is in the application
        When: he enters a specific climbing wall and goes to the "My leagues" section 
              and selects one of the leagues where he is registered,
        Then: he will be able to view the selected gym with its characteristics